header.gameNote: SOUTH PADRE ISLAND INVITATIONAL AT SOUTH PADRE ISLAND TX

article.headline: East Tennessee State 66, Southern University 52
article.story: SOUTH PADRE ISLAND, Texas (AP) -- Courtney Pigram scored 20 points to lead East Tennessee State past Southern 66-52 Saturday in a South Padre Island Invitational consolation game. Brad Nuckles added 16 points and Andrew Reed had 15 for the Buccaneers (3-4). Deforrest Riley-Smith led Southern (0-5) with 14 points. Douglas Scott added 13. Southern committed 24 turnovers that led to 27 points for East Tennessee State, which led 45-26 at halftime. The Buccaneers held a double-figure lead most of the second half. Southern narrowed the lead to nine when Scott sank a pair of free throws with 8:55 remaining, but the Jaguars quickly fell behind by double digits again.
